PrecisAmendment (SCHEDULE No. 958) to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS which allows for the use of the enzyme chymosin B produced by a modified strain of Kluyveromyces marxianus in the making of the same foods in which rennet and chymosin A and B are permitted.

precis:
Amendment (SCHEDULE No. 958) to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS which allows
for the use of the enzyme chymosin B produced by a modified strain of
Kluyveromyces marxianus in the making of the same foods in which rennet and
chymosin A and B are permitted.
